  "description": "Designed for raw field recordings and environmental audio: wind, water, insects, traffic. Very low selectivity broadens the analysis band to capture the full spectral mass of complex natural soundscapes. Slow reactivity and long memory extract large-scale amplitude movement — the way a forest swells in wind or a rain shower peaks and decays.",
